{"tid":705789,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"\"死也該看簡體中文, 被中國同化沒關係\" 台灣思想, 是蠢還是聰明?","createTime":"2018-06-17T12:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T05:29:20.000Z","uid":147756,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d218961127eec56f89015671dcec3033c1f900","tid":705789,"uid":147756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【密技】拒絕半強迫查看簡中資源, 自行決定Google搜尋結果(Chrome)</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;snA=495832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60030%26snA%3D495832&d=qk5jPCq5806TQkVFI%2BHgWO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b7faed0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;snA=495832</a></span><br />\n<br />\n台灣巴哈姆特不像LIHKG這邊一樣給<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 給得很習慣.<br />\n所以要是真的給出了, 基本上就是完全否定對方才會出現.<br />\n<br />\n目前不知道有多少五毛黨, 或者使用蝗語的人在巴哈活動.<br />\n<br />\n但這篇文章的部分反應, 很<ins><strong>明顯就是一堆人認為自己死也該看簡體中文資源</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n拼命捍衛簡體中文, 就算後面代表著中國文化也照樣捍衛<br />\n幾乎就等於 &quot;<strong>死也該看簡體中文, 被中國同化沒關係</strong>&quot; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對此台灣人想法, 港友們如何看呢?</strong><br />\n<br />\n台灣人愚蠢 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣人聰明 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227f9862f3cdecad57e83b1240ecc51e7f6c5d16","tid":705789,"uid":85659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"台狗10個有7-8個愈老愈華<br />\n我就見識過唔少,平時扮到好撚反共,少少野就露哂底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6772dbc76eee325e5207c3b73da8de68126d4b","tid":705789,"uid":147756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227f9862f3cdecad57e83b1240ecc51e7f6c5d16","tid":705789,"uid":85659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201